-- Fujitsu, Toshiba Plan to Integrate Mobile Phone Operations, Nikkei Reports
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-06-16T19:08:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/fujitsu-toshiba-plan-to-integrate-mobile-phone-operations-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Fujitsu Ltd. and Toshiba Corp.
agreed to integrate their celluar telephone businesses and they
may form a joint venture as early as October, Nikkei English
News reported, without saying how it got the information.  
 Fujitsu will hold a majority stake in the joint venture,
Nikkei said.  
          
          


  


        